image_analysis.description: A photograph showing the interior of a closet or storage cabinet. The top shelf contains two white female torso mannequins. The middle shelf contains athletic gear including a pair of dark sneakers, a blue bag, and a white towel. The bottom visible shelf contains a black storage bin with labels, stacks of small packaged items (possibly 'EverGel' hand wraps), and other blue athletic equipment.
